est.com";}i:20;a:11:{s:7:"keyword";s:25:"the chair netflix preview";s:4:"slug";s:25:"the-chair-netflix-preview";s:5:"title";s:86:"Dogs Of Berlin Trailer Coming To Netflix December 7 2018 Berlin Netflix Dramas Netflix";s:3:"alt";s:9:"pinterest";s:3:"url";s:76:"https://i.pinimg.com/originals/b9/12/35/b91235a9a875faecbd44ee3444ea96dc.png";s:5:"thumb";s:90:"https://encrypted-tbn0.gstatic.com/images?q=tbn:ANd9GcTSPEeCabOyDfLhp0ywFGQidI0yiIEwPvX3rg";s:8:"filetype";s:3:"png";s:5:"width";i:567;s:6:"height";i:1170;s:6:"source";s:49:"https://www.pinterest.com/pin/176766354111176563/";s:6:"domain";s:17:"www.pinterest.com";}}s:9:"sentences";a:56:{i:0;s:113:"Sandra Oh has played a lot of memorable characters over her more than two decades in show businessBut playing Dr.";i:1;s:151:"Ji-Yoon Kim in the upcoming Netflix comedy series The Chair still marked a unique experience for the Golden Globe and Screen Actors Guild award winner.";i:2;s:119:"I feel like Ji-Yoon is the closest character to myself that Ive ever played Oh says with a nod to showrunner executive.";i:3;s:17:"The Chair Review.";i:4;s:50:"Netflix Series Starring Sandra Oh Misses the Mark.";i:5;s:162:"Sandra Oh is the new chair of the prestigious Pembroke Universitys English Department on The Chair and that casting alone made this a show I was excited to watch.";i:6;s:103:"Unfortunately The Chair is wildly disappointing in large part because it tries to do too much with too.";i:7;s:77:"Ill Buy the Popcorns host Stephanie reviews Netflixs newest series THE CHAIR.";i:8;s:73:"Starring Sandra Oh Holland Taylor Jay Duplass Everly Carganilla David Mo.";i:9;s:30:"2021 TV-MA 1 Season TV Dramas.";i:10;s:152:"At a major university the first woman of color to become chair tries to meet the dizzying demands and high expectations of a failing English department.";i:11;s:37:"Sandra Oh Jay Duplass Holland Taylor.";i:12;s:135:"What Sandra Oh endures among the backstabbing academics and a generation of too-easily-triggered college students in The Chair Netflix.";i:13;s:167:"Netflixs The Chair with Sandra Oh is a wacky insightful look at higher education The six-episode series deals with a variety of serious issues in a fairly nuanced way.";i:14;s:38:"Joshua Axelrod August 21 2021 Updated.";i:15;s:23:"August 23 2021 1050 am.";i:16;s:21:"Preview Roush Review.";i:17;s:104:"Sandra Oh Occupies a Wobbly Academic Chair June 30 135 pm First Look at Sandra Oh in Netflixs The Chair.";i:18;s:72:"Now she headlines another series this time for Netflix titled The Chair.";i:19;s:67:"According to the official plot synopsis from the streaming service.";i:20;s:21:"The Chair follows Dr.";i:21;s:126:"Ji-Yoon Kim Sandra Oh as she navigates her new role as the Chair of the English department at prestigious Pembroke University.";i:22;s:38:"Ji-Yoon is faced with a unique set of.";i:23;s:41:"Created by Amanda Peet Annie Julia Wyman.";i:24;s:51:"With Sandra Oh Jay Duplass Bob Balaban Nana Mensah.";i:25;s:152:"At a major university the first woman of color to become chair tries to meet the dizzying demands and high expectations of a failing English department.";i:26;s:67:"The Chair Filming Locations Is Pembroke University a Real Location.";i:27;s:60:"Sadly Pembroke University is a fictional place of education.";i:28;s:62:"The Netflix series was primarily filmed in the American state.";i:29;s:245:"C reated and written by Amanda Peet and produced by Game of Thrones EPs David Benioff and DB Weiss The Chair centers around Ji-Yoon Sandra Oh the first woman of color to become head of the English department at the fictional Pembroke University.";i:30;s:134:"With the responsibility of representing a more progressive future for the prestigious school looming large shes forced to balance the.";i:31;s:155:"Ji-Yoon is faced with a unique set of challenges as the first woman to chair the department and as one of the few staff members of color at the university.";i:32;s:69:"MHOTC can preview the first three episodes of the new Netflix series.";i:33;s:45:"Winners will receive advance screening links.";i:34;s:141:"Sandra Oh has her hands full with both a college controversy and a questionable crush as the title character in the Netflix comedy The Chair.";i:35;s:36:"The full trailer above previews the.";i:36;s:291:"While Sandra Oh plays the lead in Netflixs The Chair there are times during the dramedys first season when it seems like shes been replacedThe tension between delivering a warm and funny character study and telling a story about controversial current issues ultimately tears The Chair apart.";i:37;s:70:"As the six-episode season progresses it moves away from its strengths.";i:38;s:135:"Sandra Ohs Ji-Yoon Kim makes academic history in Netflixs The Chair premiere but her achievement comes with some serious drawbacks too.";i:39;s:115:"Starring Sandra Oh the show follows the newly appointed head of a failing English department at a major university.";i:40;s:63:"Jay Duplass Holland Taylor and Bob Balaban play her colleagues.";i:41;s:21:"The Chair on Netflix.";i:42;s:127:"Beyond those two shows the Netflix teen mystery series Outer Banks remains popular on the platform taking the third place spot.";i:43;s:343:"I wanted to read novels and poems as long as I could Ji-Yoon Kim Sandra Oh tells her daughter Ju-Ju Everly Carganilla when asked why she became a professorAs the new Netflix series The Chair co-created by Amanda Peet and Annie Wyman unfolds we see how the business of academics can so easily obfuscate the passions of those who work within it.";i:44;s:174:"Recently the biggest and famous Over-The-Top OTT platform Netflix came up with a fantastic and hilarious streaming TV series named The Chair to excite and amuse the audience.";i:45;s:152:"The series has already been released for the viewers on the official streaming website of Netflix and so far it is getting a positive response from the.";i:46;s:164:"Netflix is about to release its latest original series The ChairThe dramedy focuses on the